<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="K" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Keel1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Keel,</orth> subst. the principal timber in a ship, which supports the whole frame; used for the whole ship: <bibl n="shak. oth 2.1.70" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. II, 1, 70</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 1.4.50" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. I, 4, 50</bibl>. Per. <bibl n="shak. ant 3.0." default="NO" valid="yes">III Prol. 46</bibl>.
